{"tid":1599955,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"政治市時代 必吼三大板塊","createTime":"2019-09-28T10:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T02:02:08.000Z","uid":174649,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cf01c99e11d62ecd4d9cd575e1b32e0476312c56","tid":1599955,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T10:50:48.000Z","msg":"香港經濟政策<br />\n<br />\n早前有政策提出引用收回土地條例起公屋，最新團結香港基金則提出「港人組屋」。不論如何，基建股必先受惠。當中，瑞安建業（983）參與興建公營房屋接近四十年經驗，大量建公屋將會受惠。至於基建工程，承接本港各項相關工程的利基控股（0240）應最直接受惠，並一度成為明日大嶼填海概念股；另外，收入35%來自香港的中國建築（3311）亦承接香港政府的房屋及土木工程，料亦將有憧憬。至於被收回土地的地產股，收回土地可帶來短線盈利，但失去土儲又會影響長遠發展業務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190928/60089550\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190928%2F60089550&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj93lGhCGuGi3hvupoSMmYHA%3D&h=51bfd0ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190928%2F60089550&h=06641d34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190928/60089550</a>"},{"pid":"477343a62dcfe3548f5631e1c618757e3f1adf85","tid":1599955,"uid":55533,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直接買etf好撚過啦<br />\n港股已經a股化<br />\n仲買個股黎被大戶劏咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7953b1697dd8f8a5d4c18932fef2a8fc5d1bfbb1","tid":1599955,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T15:15:05.000Z","msg":"282先係"},{"pid":"2764386b16274e2a02464ba2e7feedead0cbd138","tid":1599955,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T16:45:06.000Z","msg":"個圖西到傻散都唔會落踏啦<img src=\"